<http://localhost/resource/exe-36>
    rdf:type              test:Executor ;
    test:deliveryAddress  <http://localhost/resource/addr-160> , <http://localhost/resource/addr-183> ;
    <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/familyName>
                          "Hmm. In the end, cowards are those who follow the dark side." , "Like fire across the galaxy the Clone Wars spread. In league with the wicked Count Dooku, more and more planets slip. Against this threat, upon the Jedi Knights falls the duty to lead the newly formed army of the Republic. And as the heat of war grows, so, to, grows the prowess of one most gifted student of the Force." ;
    <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/givenName>
                          "The dark side clouds everything. Impossible to see the future is." , "Younglings, younglings gather â€™round." ;
    <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/name>
                          "Always pass on what you have learned." , "Pain, suffering, death I feel. Something terrible has happened. Young Skywalker is in pain. Terrible pain" .

